uss the physical working\nprinciples of PFM and develop a strategy to extract physical meaning from the\nPFM phase. The proposed procedures are verified on two materials with positive\nand negative piezoelectric coefficients.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 Dec 2019 17:55:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-09"}
