c nanotracks with\nstrategically modified magnetic properties. Furthermore, we discuss in detail 6\nways to suppress the skyrmion Hall effect by the usage of nanotracks with\nrepulsive edges and nanotracks with an attractive strip.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 7 Dec 2019 01:09:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 14 Feb 2020 21:19:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-27"}
