uld guide the development of indirect\nbacteriotherapies, which seek to change microbial compositions by deliberately\nmodifying gut environmental variables such as gut acidity or macronutrient\navailability.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 7 Dec 2019 02:04:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 29 Mar 2020 06:02:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-13"}
