 is thus\nable to obtain improved radar performance, as demonstrated in our simulation\nstudy. Furthermore, the proposed dual-function scheme approaches the radar\nperformance of the radar-only scheme, i.e., without spectrum sharing, under\nreasonable communication quality constraints.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 7 Dec 2019 02:51:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 2 Feb 2020 04:26:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-26"}
